Main components
- rankserver: web server (listens on http/4001, https/4002 by default)
- dfticker: periodic data fetcher
- twitter_ticker: periodic twitter poster

Dependency
- make
- Go
- Perl
- msgpack: "github.com/ugorji/go/codec"
- lz4: "github.com/bkaradzic/go-lz4"
- sqlite3: "github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3"
- yaml: "gopkg.in/yaml.v2"
- Net::Twitter: Perl module
- [optional] gopacket: "github.com/google/gopacket"

To run a full service
- write config files
- make fetch
- make server
- make twitter

